            "icon": "none",
            "heading": "How long does shipping take?",
            "content": "<p>Shipping typically takes 5-7 business days within the United States. For international orders, shipping can take 10-15 business days, depending on the destination and customs processing times. You will receive a tracking number once your order has shipped so you can monitor its progress.</p>",
