            "icon": "none",
            "heading": "Do you ship internationally?",
            "content": "<p>Yes, we do ship internationally! We offer worldwide shipping to ensure customers around the globe can enjoy our skincare products. Please note that shipping times and costs may vary depending on the destination country. International customers may also be subject to customs fees or import duties imposed by their country's customs authorities.</p>",
            "custom_liquid": "",
            "page": "",
